{"tid":2160904,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"科大成為學術界馬英九 合作公司非死即傷","createTime":"2020-08-17T09:07:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-17T12:13:12.000Z","uid":225931,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"32f7e23a4e1b88f95719b4f49c92ca7e64301ed1","tid":2160904,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"HKUST-BGI Joint Research Center<br />\n美國商務部公布制裁11間內地企業，包括知名的歐菲光、華大基因，美國商務部指，11間企業涉及配合官方侵犯人權、大規模任意拘留、強迫勞動，並對維吾爾自治區穆斯林少數民族強制收集生物識別數據。<br />\n<br />\nHKUST-DJI Joint Innovation Laboratory<br />\n由於受疫情影響及主要市場的政治壓力，大疆的裁員計劃始於今年3月份，擬削減三分之二的行銷和銷售人員。有知情人士透露，大疆深圳總部的企業銷售和營銷團隊從180人削減至60人，在消費者團隊也在裁減人員。全球視頻製作團隊也由50人縮減至約 3人。<br />\n<br />\nHKUST-NAVER/LINE AI Lab<br />\n出於對隱私問題的擔憂，Naver 近日證實將放棄香港做為資料備份中心的基地，改為轉移至新加坡擴展站點。<br />\n<br />\nHKUST-Xiaoi Robot Joint Lab on Machine Learning and Cognitive Reasoning<br />\n智臻智能向上海高級人民法院提起訴訟，稱蘋果公司在其iPhone的語音助理軟件Siri中未經允許使用了該公司的專利技術，侵犯了它的一項被編號為&ldquo;ZL200410053749.9&rdquo;的發明專利權。<br />\n<br />\nHuawei-HKUST Innovation Laboratory<br />\n被美國制裁<br />\n<br />\nWeChat-HKUST Joint Lab on Artificial Intelligence Technology (WHAT LAB)<br />\n被美國封殺"},{"pid":"16afcb468ef563657e8f13957c647c4ba16f3c77","tid":2160904,"uid":51200,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:14:33.000Z","msg":"學術界馬英九<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3044ad2fdc5536e3d407320c4b7a78dd232b709b","tid":2160904,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T09:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14839e6562711dfd99942ee84692f05d828bee4b","tid":2160904,"uid":165700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-17T0